MeshChat64 — Commodore Callback 8020 App
=========================================

ATTRIBUTION

All MeshChat application code is authored by saint-cc.
Upstream repository: https://github.com/saint-cc/meshchat

This includes, without exception: server.py, script.js (the entire
chat/crypto/relay client), statemachine.js, sw.js, index.html, the original
style.css, and the MeshChat protocol design (encrypted relay chat, the
shareable-key format, cross-relay delivery).

This repository is strictly a presentation and compatibility layer on top of
saint-cc's code, published with his permission. It never forks or modifies his
source; the deploy pipeline mirrors his main branch pristine and re-applies
the overlay at build time. Nothing in this repository relicenses any part of
upstream MeshChat.

